CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is populated by a user or a data integration. If true, the owner is not an individual claiming treaty benefits for dividends received from a foreign corporation or interest from a US trade or business of a foreign corporation and meets qualified resident status. It is form-specific for the W-8BEN (Certificate of Foreign Status of Beneficial Owner for United States Tax Withholding).
CustomField.inlineHelpText: If true the owner is not an individual is claiming treaty benefits for dividends.
CustomField.label: Form W8 Treaty Qualified Resident Status
